-- Salini Impregilo shares up nearly 3 pct after new business plan
-- 
-- Thu Mar 20, 2014 04:17AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, March 20 (Reuters) - Shares in Italy's biggest construction group Salini Impregilo <SALI.MI> rallied nearly 3 percent in early trading on Thursday after the company said it aimed to double core profit by 2017.

